💻 2. SNAPSHOT SYSTEM

👉 Vor und nach Node-Ausführung messen:

class Snapshot {
    int p;
    int i;
    int s;
    double survival;

    public Snapshot(int p, int i, int s) {
        this.p = p;
        this.i = i;
        this.s = s;
        this.survival = (double)(i + s) / (p + 1);
    }
}

